Class SignUpService

java.lang.Object
CSC540.WolfWR.services.Services<SignUp,Long>
CSC540.WolfWR.services.SignUpService
@Transactional @Component public class SignUpService extends Services<SignUp,Long>
Service class responsible for handling operations related to SignUp entities.

This class extends the generic Services class and provides CRUD operations for managing SignUp entities. It interacts with the SignUpRepository to perform operations such as saving, finding, and deleting SignUp records from the database.
